examples.en: The theater is dark on Mondays.
Garbage pickup is on Mondays and Thursdays.
The programme goes out live at 5 o'clock on Mondays.
Some of the staff are apt to arrive late on Mondays.
Our figure skating club has exclusive use of the rink on Mondays.
Professor Lee's office hours are from 2 to 4 on Mondays and Thursdays.
